text: Dices on ðeodweg norð ofer þone weg.
Þanan east to freccehlince of þam hlince to halignesse beorge of þam beorge east to <stæ>.
Garan of þam garan to þam byrgelsan of þæm byrgelsan to billingabyrig & swa andlang <læse>.

And ða dænn ærest þær scealces burna & bollanea hi gegaderiað on norðhealfe wæs
.
Þis is seo landboc þe nunna cyng gebocade eadberhte <biscope> into hugabeorgum,xxhida.
